<p><a href="https://cn.comsol.com/video/performing-a-parameter-estimation-study-in-comsol-multiphysics" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">在 COMSOL Multiphysics<sup>®</sup> 中运行“参数估计”研究</a></p>
